CompetitionMetaData.Help:
This Competition implements a protocol using polar coordinates PX {l} {a} {r} {g} {b} - or - PX {l} {a} #{color}
l: distance to the center a: angle given as ten-thousands of a full circle (1/10000) r: red color component of a pixel g: green color component of a pixel b: blue color component of a pixel
color: color encoded as a html color (rgb-values as hex)
